  "field_frequency": {
    "en": 20,
    "example": 1,
    "invest in eden house dubai hills, dubai hills estate, dubai": 1,
    "invest in eden house dubai hills": 1,
    "eden house dubai hills": 1,
    "register your interest": 1,
    "about eden house dubai hills": 1,
    "elite 5 bedroom villas in dubai hills estate": 1,
    "eden house dubai hills presents an exclusive collection of 5 bedroom villas designed by renowned hopkins architects. set within dubai hills estate's verdant landscapes, these masterfully crafted residences span up to 7,820 sq. ft on generous plots reaching 10,969 sq. ft. each villa features private gardens, pools, elevators, and premium finishes, complemented by world class community amenities.": 1,
    "crafted by world renowned hopkins architects": 1,
    "eden house dubai hills bears the signature excellence of hopkins architects, a globally acclaimed architectural firm known for creating timeless designs. their masterful approach combines contemporary aesthetics with sustainable principles, ensuring each villa stands as a testament to architectural brilliance.": 1,
    "living in nature's paradise": 1,
    "eden house dubai hills is nestled within dubai hills estate's lush landscapes, offering residents a rare connection with nature.": 1,
    "private garden retreats": 1,
    "each villa features meticulously landscaped private gardens creating personal outdoor sanctuaries.": 1,
    "panoramic rooftop views": 1,
    "select villas offer stunning rooftop terraces overlooking dubai's iconic skyline.": 1,
    "and also": 1,
    "swimming pool": 1,
    "fitness center": 1,
    "spa center": 1,
    "landscaped gardens": 1,
    "h&h development": 1,
    "h&h development, founded in 2007, is a comprehensive real estate developer known for its \"all in one\" approach to asset management and luxury developments. the company specializes in high end projects across dubai, including four seasons private residences and baccarat hotel and residences, while focusing on technical expertise, cost optimization, and innovative design to create value for investors.": 1,
    "premium dubai hills estate address": 1,
    "transport accessibility": 1,
    "located adjacent to al khail road, eden house dubai hills offers 20 minute access to downtown dubai and business bay, with dubai international airport just 25 minutes away.": 1,
    "nearest attractions": 1,
    "minutes from dubai hills golf club's 18 hole championship course, dubai hills mall with 650+ shops, and dubai hills park   the longest park in dubai's residential communities.": 1,
    "developed infrastructure": 1,
    "premium educational facilities including gems international school, gems wellington academy, and king's college hospital are within a 10 minute drive.": 1,
    "premium location appeal": 1,
    "dubai hills estate offers incredible connectivity to dubai's key destinations. the community enjoys a strategic location adjacent to al khail road, providing swift access to dubai's business and leisure hubs. the development's limited collection of villas, designed by hopkins architects, ensures exclusivity and value appreciation. with 5 bedroom villas in dubai hills estate commanding annual rents of aed 320k (usd 87k), investors can expect strong returns backed by growing demand for luxury family homes.": 1,
    "eden house villa ownership provides eligibility for dubai's 10 year golden visa, extending to family members and household staff. this grants comprehensive benefits including emirates id, banking access, and streamlined government services   enabling seamless access to dubai's lifestyle amenities and essential services.": 1,
    "eng": 1
  },
